# IntentParameter.ValueState

**Enumeration**

Indicates whether an IntentParameter was provided an initial value or if it was unset

## Declaration

```swift
enum ValueState
```

## Enumeration Cases

- **IntentParameter.ValueState.set(_:)**: The parameter was provided an initial value.
- **IntentParameter.ValueState.unset**: The parameter was never provided a value

## Accessing the underlying value

- **defaultValue**
- **projectedValue**
- **wrappedValue**
- **valueState**: Check if an IntentParameter was provided an initial value

## Conforms To

- Copyable
- Equatable
